subject: Baseball
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: The town of Cairo, Ga., has two streets named for prominent native sons: Jackie Robinson Memorial Drive and Willie Harris Drive. That’s a distinction that Harris, a left fielder for the Braves, proudly shares.
